# ui-tests runs against the standalone Storage Explorer webview (Vite dev server), driven by
# Playwright. Copy this file to `ui-tests/.env`. It is gitignored — never commit tokens.
#
# DEFAULT (no vars set) => MOCK mode: Microsoft Graph is mocked and the full UI flow runs
# deterministically with no tenant. Ideal for CI and for validating the UI/harness.
#
# LIVE mode: set SPE_TEST_ACCESS_TOKEN (a real Graph delegated token with
# FileStorageContainer.Selected for your testing tenant) AND SPE_TEST_CONTAINER_TYPE_ID.
# The test then hits the REAL Graph API and creates a real container.

# SPE_TEST_ACCESS_TOKEN=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1Qi...        # real Graph bearer token (enables LIVE mode)
# SPE_TEST_CONTAINER_TYPE_ID=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
# SPE_TEST_REGISTRATION_ID=
# SPE_TEST_TENANT_DOMAIN=contoso.onmicrosoft.com
# SPE_TEST_WEB_PORT=5178
